name: "STYLIST"
description:
I've chosen four creative, talented women, got my friend Camilla to take their picture and have placed their photo on to a tee. I think that the fact that it's a photographic image rather than a graphic makes it have longevity.
"Stylist" is Irene. She's styled a lot of music video's from Lethal B to Natty to Sincere. She's also done a lot of editorial styling for a variety of magazine's. Definitely one to watch! Keep an eye out!!! check out her website www.eyesbehindshades.com
